  // Sebastian /////////////////////////
  "Mail.MTV_SebQ1": "I hear you've been doing some pretty freaky things around town, and I was hoping you could help me out with something. I've always had a thing for Abigail, particularly since she started her streams online. Do you think you could get me some of her milk? Fresh from the source?^^Thanks. Sebastian %item quest 594809 %%",
  "Mail.MTV_SebQ1T": "Hey there perv.^So....I know that Seb has been on my streams, and in hindsight I'm guessing the milk was for him? For someone so concerned with online anonymity, he's terrible at sneaking around in real life.^Anyway, I think that we should have some fun with him soon but he'll definitely enjoy it...mostly.^Abigail",

  "Mail.MTV_SebQ2": "Time for revenge, @.^^Don't worry, it's a good kind of revenge, and I think both you and Seb will like it. If he's gonna watch me on my streams, say nothing, and then act all stalker-y then we're going to play with him a bit. Can you give him a BJ, and bring me his cum?^^I think that will do for today.^ ^_^ Abigail~ %item quest 594810 %%",
  "Mail.MTV_SebQ2T": "Hey there, @.^^I wish I could have seen his face last night as I told the stream that I was drinking the cum of 'darkcoder420' live on stream. I think he shut his entire computer down, he was gone so fast! So I'd say mission accomplished.^Abigail",

  "Mail.MTV_SebQ3": "Hey, @.^^Me and Demetrius have been trying to get Seb out of his room for a few days now but he just thinks we're just trying to get him to \"be one with nature\". Is there anything you can do to get him to see the sun for the first time in a week?^^Robin. %item quest 594811 %%",
  "Mail.MTV_SebQ3T": "@,^^Thanks for yesterday. It didn't exactly change my world view but seeing you outside, completely comfortable being naked in nature...that's something I'd like to see more of. Not that i'm trying to creep on you, i just meant that it felt good.^^Seb.",

  "Mail.MTV_SebQ4": "To a really special friend,^^I'm really hoping you'd come somewhere special with me. It's always been the one place outside that I feel I'm not judged, or that I feel out of place. Can you meet me outside my house tonight, after 11pm? I promise you it'll be worth it.^^Sebastian %item quest 594812 %%",
