  "Mail.MTV_PennyQ1T": "Dear @.^^Thank you for help me out with that situation in the library. I promise I'll be more careful from now on, though my mother has been asking me so many questions lately.^I'm sure she suspects something, so I may have to find a new place to read my book.^Anyway, I hope that you'll keep this a secret between us.^Penny.",

  "Mail.MTV_PennyQ2": "Greetings loyal customer!^^Here is the delivery of your recent purchase, Order No. 598426. If you have any issues, or are dissatisfied with your purchase in any way, please log in to our online portal to arrange a pickup.^Hoping you have a wonderful, 'full-filling' day,^^Personal Companions^(Getting to know you INTIMATELY)^^^PS. We left your package just outside your main gate, in case you didn't want anyone to see it.' %item quest 594826 %%",
  "Mail.MTV_PennyQ2T": "Greetings loyal customer^^We apologise for the recent mis-delivery of a 'discrete, personal massager TM' There is no need to return this item - once used all of our items are the property of the person using them.^^There is no charge, so please consider this a free sample.^^Discrete Companions^(Getting to know you INTIMATELY)",

  "Mail.MTV_PennyQ3": "Psst.^^Come by the bath house in the evenings. You MIGHT see something...special. (If you look in the windows)^^      -Anonymous.^^PS. Don't get caught! %item quest 594827 %%",
  "Mail.MTV_PennyQ3P": "Hey there, @.^^I don't know if you saw anything at the bath house last night but I head someone rustling around in the bushes out there while I was soaking last night.^   Penny.^^PS. If you want to join me next time, I'll be inside.",
  "Mail.MTV_PennyQ3T": "I'm more than a little nervous about how last night might change our relationship. I've never really seen you as a dominant kind of person, what with how kind and considerate you are.^But last night changed that for me, and I don't think I can go back, now that I've seen you like that.^^Penny",

