  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ1": "Helo farmer @.^^Shane has bean rily sad and i want to ask yuo too help make him happier.^Plese help him.^^Jasmine%item quest 594841 %%",
  "Quests.594841.01": "A distraction for Shane",
