  "Quests.594841.03": "See if you can find Shane and cheer him up",
  "Quests.594841.09": "Thanks, @. I'm not sure what I was thinking about before but it doesn't seem as bad now.",
  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ1T": "Thank you for helping Shane.^^He is happyer again.^^-Jasmine",

  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ2": "Hi farmer,^^   Your visit really helped but I think I need to call a cheat day - just one day where I don't have to hold back so I don't give in worse. I don't really want to let anyone else seeing me get a JojaCola because of the looks they'd give me, so if you can bring one for me then maybe we can hang out a bit today?.^I promise this is just the one, and you'll be there to help me keep everything under control, right?^^-Shane%item quest 594842 %%",
  "Quests.594842.01": "Riding the forbidden high",
  "Quests.594842.02": "Shane has asked for your help having a 'cheat' day.",
  "Quests.594842.03": "Bring Shane a JojaCola",
  "Quests.594842.09": "I know that wasn't the smart thing to do but it definitely helps me today.",
  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ2T": "So I guess the cheat day wasn't the brightest idea I've had. Thanks for being there with me, and for not judging me. You're really special, @.^Maybe, check in on me now and again? If you don't mind, that is.",

  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ3": "Hey there @.^^This is going to sound awkward. I've never been much of a writer and I guess I'm pretty bad at it.^Basically, I'm hoping we can hang out sometime soon. Life is...tough. And it doesn't suck as much when you're around. If you want to hang out I'm usually around the cliffs south of the forest. Bring a drink if you want.^^Thanks %item quest 594843 %%",
  "Quests.594843.01": "Faded blue dreams",
  "Quests.594843.02": "Shane has asked you to sit with him by the cliffs in Cindersnap forest",
  "Quests.594843.03": "Go hang out with Shane in the forest",
  "Quests.594843.09": "Thanks for being with me, @. It's not easy admitting that life is getting harder again when everyone is so happy that I'm doing well.",
  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ3T": "...Thanks for hanging out with me, @. You make life not suck as much.^^Shane",

  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ4": "How's it going, @?^^I feel like the last few weeks have been a bit better and easier. You keep popping up every time I have a really bad day, and you help me get through them.^Anyway, I was thinking we could do something to 'celebrate'? I don't know, maybe it's dumb but I was thinking that we could do something fun that gives us a good memory.^^-Shane^^PS. No JojaCola this time, I swear.%item quest 594844 %%",
  "Quests.594844.01": "Good time memories",
  "Quests.594844.02": "It sounds like Shane wants to celebrate looking forward to the future. Modestly, of course.",
  "Quests.594844.03": "Go see Shane in the forest and help him make some positive memories.",
  "Quests.594844.09": "@, you really help me see a brighter future.#$b#I hope you'll be in my future for a long time.",
  "Mail.MTV_ShaneQ4T": "I really enjoyed our hangout @. You're the best thing in my life. Seriously.^^-Shane",


